<i>noun</i>: 대응책 [대ː응책] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>대응책 [대ː응책]</dt><br>
<dd>countermeasure; action</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 상황에 알맞은 태도나 행동을 취하기 위한 대책.</dd><br>
<dd>A measure for adopting the appropriate attitude or taking the appropriate action in a certain situation.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>